         <div type="commentary">
            <head>Commentary</head>
            <p>For a description and discussion of the statue and the sculptor see Brinkerhoff ap. 
               Kraeling, 183, 196.12 and, more recently, see Fabbricotti. <!-- line c. ? check -->. 
            </p>
            <p>It is possible that the statue originally stood in 
               the Odeon where three dedications by Kominios were found, <ref type="inscription">P09300</ref>,  <ref type="inscription">P09900</ref>, <ref type="inscription">P10000</ref>. 
